title: Demacion Justice looking for players

embed.description: Demacian Justice is recruiting new players to start a competitive team in OCE. We are looking for high elo people who are at least above D4 last...

body:
Hi, we are looking to form a new team in the OCE region. If you think you are qualified, you can leave a comment here, add my smurf: The Only Latvian or leave a comment on Reddit, cheers!

https://www.reddit.com/r/TeamRedditTeams/comments/7t9eeu/oced4starting_a_competitive_team/
